      "id": "81407791",
      "title": "📣 PVHS Wellness Center | Mindful Movement Workshop at Lunch with CAPSLO on 5/27/26",
      "summary": "In recognition of Mental Health Awareness Month, we’re excited to welcome CAPSLO to host a special lunchtime workshop in the Wellness Center on Wednesday, May 27. During this interactive session, C...",
      "date": "2026-05-22",
      "author": "Crystal Buchan",
      "url": "https://www.parentsquare.com/feeds/81407791",
      "pinned": false,
      "body": "<span style=\"color:rgb(42, 45, 47);font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);display:inline !important;float:none;\">In recognition of Mental Health Awareness Month, we’re excited to welcome CAPSLO to host a special lunchtime workshop in the Wellness Center on Wednesday, May 27.</span><br style=\"color:rgb(42, 45, 47);font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color:rgb(42, 45, 47);font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);display:inline !important;float:none;\">During this interactive session, CAPSLO will guide students through:</span><br style=\"color:rgb(42, 45, 47);font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br style=\"color:rgb(42, 45, 47);font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color:rgb(42, 45, 47);font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);display:inline !important;float:none;\">Mindful meditation</span><br style=\"color:rgb(42, 45, 47);font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color:rgb(42, 45, 47);font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);display:inline !important;float:none;\">Light stretching and movement</span><br style=\"color:rgb(42, 45, 47);font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color:rgb(42, 45, 47);font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);display:inline !important;float:none;\">A discussion on the importance of self-care and physical movement for mental health</span><br style=\"color:rgb(42, 45, 47);font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br style=\"color:rgb(42, 45, 47);font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color:rgb(42, 45, 47);font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);display:inline !important;float:none;\">This is a great opportunity to unwind, decompress, and learn simple strategies to support your well-being (see flyer for more details).</span><br style=\"color:rgb(42, 45, 47);font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br style=\"color:rgb(42, 45, 47);font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color:rgb(42, 45, 47);font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);display:inline !important;float:none;\">Important Details:</span><br style=\"color:rgb(42, 45, 47);font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br style=\"color:rgb(42, 45, 47);font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color:rgb(42, 45, 47);font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);display:inline !important;float:none;\">Location: PVHS Wellness Center</span><br style=\"color:rgb(42, 45, 47);font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color:rgb(42, 45, 47);font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);display:inline !important;float:none;\">Time: Lunch</span><br style=\"color:rgb(42, 45, 47);font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color:rgb(42, 45, 47);font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);display:inline !important;float:none;\">Space is limited to the first 25 students</span><br style=\"color:rgb(42, 45, 47);font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color:rgb(42, 45, 47);font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);display:inline !important;float:none;\">Goodies will be provided to those who attend!</span><br style=\"color:rgb(42, 45, 47);font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br style=\"color:rgb(42, 45, 47);font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color:rgb(42, 45, 47);font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);display:inline !important;float:none;\">Sign Ups Required:</span><br style=\"color:rgb(42, 45, 47);font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color:rgb(42, 45, 47);font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);display:inline !important;float:none;\">Sign up in the Wellness Center with Mrs. Buchan or Ms. Collins on:</span><br style=\"color:rgb(42, 45, 47);font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br style=\"color:rgb(42, 45, 47);font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color:rgb(42, 45, 47);font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);display:inline !important;float:none;\">Tuesday, May 26 (before 9:30 AM), or</span><br style=\"color:rgb(42, 45, 47);font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color:rgb(42, 45, 47);font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);display:inline !important;float:none;\">Wednesday, May 27 (before the end of break)</span><br style=\"color:rgb(42, 45, 47);font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br><span style=\"color:rgb(42, 45, 47);font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);display:inline !important;float:none;\">We hope you’ll join us for this calming and supportive experience!</span><br><span style=\"color:rgb(42, 45, 47);font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);display:inline !important;float:none;\"><img src=\"https://posts.parentsquare.com/inline_images_e696d7014cae4dd8_1779491421612-SG+Mindful+Movement+Workshop.png\" style=\"width:300px;display:block;vertical-align:top;margin:5px auto;text-align:center;\"></span>",
