      "date": "2026-05-20",
      "author": "Melani Mederos",
      "url": "https://www.parentsquare.com/feeds/81182179",
      "pinned": false,
      "body": "<span style=\"font-size:18px;\">Hey Panthers!<br><br>Allan Hancock College DualEnrollment CCAP (Concurrent Enrollment) course grades are due <strong><span style=\"color:rgb(181, 0, 0);\">Tuesday, May 26th</span></strong> before midnight. <br><br><strong>Students-</strong> Please make sure you are communicating with your teachers to ensure all of your assignments are submitted. Please be sure to be present for your final, and remember you must pass your class with the grade of a \"C\" or better to get credit.<br><br>Questions? Please contact your grade level counselor or Mrs. Mederos in the College &amp; Career Center. <br><br>Good luck on your finals and finish strong Panthers!</span>",
      "images": [
        "https://assets.parentsquare.com/assets/1906392-0ac1512e7/home/parentsquare-c4715e668bca69cd74fedb882b80965c2801b4a972ae68c0b6b6084e21520a9a.png"
      ]
