      "id": "81112642",
      "title": "🎪 Mental Health Resource Fair | May 22",
      "summary": "PVHS Families: The Wellness Center, in partnership our SHARe and Care Club, is excited to host our annual Mental Health Resource Fair on Friday, May 22nd during lunch. This event provides a valuabl...",
      "date": "2026-05-20",
      "author": "Crystal Buchan",
      "url": "https://www.parentsquare.com/feeds/81112642",
      "pinned": false,
      "body": "<div style=\"font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;line-height:20px;\">PVHS Families:<br><br>The Wellness Center, in partnership our SHARe and Care Club, is excited to host our annual Mental Health Resource Fair on Friday, May 22nd during lunch.<br><br>This event provides a valuable opportunity for students and staff to connect with over 15 community organizations and school-based resources offering mental health education, support, and services. Our goal is to help students learn more about available resources and encourage overall well being.<br><br>Students who visit each booth will also have the chance to enter a raffle for prizes!<br><br>We encourage all students to stop by, explore the resources, and take an active step toward supporting their mental health.<br><br><a href=\"https://canva.link/1hu9dq4dj2owqv7\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://posts.parentsquare.com/inline_images_2d05c4960bb1d4b6_1779292241926-Mental+Health+Resource+Fair+1.png\" style=\"width:300px;display:block;vertical-align:top;margin:5px auto;text-align:center;\"></a><a href=\"https://canva.link/1hu9dq4dj2owqv7\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://posts.parentsquare.com/inline_images_2d05c4960bb1d4b6_1779292250070-Mental+Health+Resource+Fair+2.png\" style=\"width:300px;display:block;vertical-align:top;margin:5px auto;text-align:center;\"></a><strong></strong>",
      "images": [
        "https://assets.parentsquare.com/assets/1906392-0ac1512e7/home/parentsquare-c4715e668bca69cd74fedb882b80965c2801b4a972ae68c0b6b6084e21520a9a.png",
        "https://posts.parentsquare.com/inline_images_2d05c4960bb1d4b6_1779292241926-Mental+Health+Resource+Fair+1.png",
        "https://posts.parentsquare.com/inline_images_2d05c4960bb1d4b6_1779292250070-Mental+Health+Resource+Fair+2.png"
      ]
