      "pinned": false,
      "body": "<p style='margin:0in 0in 8pt;color:rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family:proxima-nova, \"proxima nova\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height:15.9px;font-size:15px;text-align:center;'><span style=\"font-size:21px;line-height:22.26px;color:rgb(56, 86, 35);\">Tomorrow is College Craze Thursday!</span></p><p style='margin:0in 0in 8pt;color:rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family:proxima-nova, \"proxima nova\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height:15.9px;font-size:15px;text-align:center;'><span style=\"font-size:21px;line-height:22.26px;color:rgb(255, 192, 0);\">Remember to wear your COLLEGE gear!</span></p><p style='margin:0in 0in 8pt;color:rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family:proxima-nova, \"proxima nova\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height:15.9px;font-size:15px;text-align:center;'><span style=\"font-size:21px;line-height:22.26px;\">Teacher Spotlight</span></p><div style=\"border:0px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;line-height:inherit;margin:0px;padding:0px;vertical-align:baseline;letter-spacing:normal;text-align:center;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);color:black !important;\">Mrs. Maldonado</div><div style=\"border:0px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;line-height:inherit;margin:0px;padding:0px;vertical-align:baseline;letter-spacing:normal;text-align:center;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);color:black !important;\">Teaches all levels of Spanish, 32 years teaching in the classroom</div><div style=\"border:0px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;line-height:inherit;margin:0px;padding:0px;vertical-align:baseline;letter-spacing:normal;text-align:center;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);color:black !important;\">Stanford University, degrees in Cultural Anthropology and Chicano Studies</div><div style=\"border:0px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;line-height:inherit;margin:0px;padding:0px;vertical-align:baseline;letter-spacing:normal;text-align:center;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);color:black !important;\">One of my favorite memories is doing a scavenger hunt with my frosh dorm in San Francisco. We had to talk to all sorts of  people and do crazy things with people who would end up becoming life long friends.</div><img src=\"https://posts.parentsquare.com/inline_images_88e727265dc43ed3_1776889588660-Stanford.png\" style=\"width:300px;display:block;vertical-align:top;margin:5px auto;text-align:center;\">",
