      "id": "80416058",
      "title": "🎓 Senior Slideshow",
      "summary": "Good morning! Twenty days from today, the Class of 2026 will walk across the stage to receive their diplomas and start the next journey of their lives.",
      "date": "2026-05-13",
      "author": "Lisa Walters",
      "url": "https://www.parentsquare.com/feeds/80416058",
      "pinned": false,
      "body": "<span style=\"font-size:22px;\">Good morning!<br><br>Twenty days from today, the Class of 2026 will walk across the stage to receive their diplomas and start the next journey of their lives.  Every year, I make a senior slideshow, including pictures of seniors at all of their different ages, and long time friends who are graduating together.  <br><br>In order to do this, I need pictures!  So, please, parents, send me your childhood pictures - especially those that show friendships that have been through the years.  Students, send me the pictures of you and your friends - elementary, junior high, or high school.  Staff, send me pictures from your class, office, club, athletic team, or random event.  Here is the Google form: <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSci50BlOfWVcqkLeovKBEG_NE2dxQqFLRGA4i7FM8qA-qvrIw/viewform?usp=publish-editor\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSci50BlOfWVcqkLeovKBEG_NE2dxQqFLRGA4i7FM8qA-qvrIw/viewform?usp=publish-editor</a><br><br>If you have more than 3 pictures you want to include, please just complete another form.  I will accept as many as you can send me!<br><br>Also, I have included a question about a shout out.  I will use as many of these as possible, but the slideshow can only be 15 minutes long, because it is the last thing the seniors see before they leave the gym.  That is why the number of characters is limited.  So - parents, shout out to seniors!  Seniors - shout out to your parents!  Staff - shout out to seniors or parents!</span>",
      "images": [
        "https://assets.parentsquare.com/assets/1906392-0ac1512e7/home/parentsquare-c4715e668bca69cd74fedb882b80965c2801b4a972ae68c0b6b6084e21520a9a.png"
      ]
    }
  ]
